1485,Domingo,['Tile Placement'],['Abstract Strategy'],Not to be confused with the Ravensburger game with the same name (look here: 3 Or More) this one is named as a cross between BINGO and Dominoes.<br/><br/>The tiles are square and have a number on all 4 sides.  Players draw a tile and place it in their 5X5 tray.  All sides must match.  The first player to place 5 in a straight line wins.  Included in the box are rules for a few other variations.<br/><br/>,1982,,,;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
